an degrade the performance of the models (as\nassessed by model selection criteria). Of special relevance is the fact that\nthe inclusion of LSS data appears to increase compatibility with a flat\ngeometry. It also brings the constraints on the Hubble constant closer to the\nrange of values established by \\emph{Planck}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2018 20:28:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 Jun 2020 14:32:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-05"}
