tracting out \\marvin's core\nfunctionality into a separate product so that it can serve as a foundation for\nothers to develop \\marvin-like systems for new science applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2018 19:09:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-31"}
